sition-colors">Projects</p></a><a href="../insights"><p class="text-current font-body text-xl leading-none hover:text-yellow transition-colors">Insights</p></a><a href="../contact"><p class="text-current font-body text-xl leading-none hover:text-yellow transition-colors">Contact</p></a></div></div><div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-unit col-span-full pb-8 border-l border-current pl-unit pt-unit h-full"><div class="col-span-6 pr-6"><p class="text-current font-body text-xl">Bolt Builds is a design, build, and fabrication firm located in Greenpoint, Brooklyn.</p><div class="pt-4"><a class="block hover:text-yellow transition-colors" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&amp;query=202+Banker+Street+Brooklyn+NY+11222"><p class="text-current font-body text-xl">202 Banker Street</p><p class="text-current font-body text-xl">Brooklyn, NY 11222</p></a><a class="text-current font-body text-xl block hover:text-yellow transition-colors" href="mailto:hello@bolt.build">hello@bolt.build</a><a class="text-current font-body text-xl block hover:text-yellow transition-colors" href="tel:+1 917-740-3463">+1 917-740-3463</a></div></div></div></div><div class="col-span-2 lg:col-span-1 border-t-0 lg:border-t border-x md:border-x-0 border-current"></div></div></div><div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10"><div class="cover-image-shim absolute inset-0 z-10"></div><img src="https://www.boltdesign.nyc/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2F4j6lg3tu%2Fproduction%2F52652e63365208885f555c81484ff15eb2155f66-1447x859.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75" srcSet="https://www.boltdesign.nyc/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2F4j6lg3tu%2Fproduction%2F52652e63365208885f555c81484ff15eb2155f66-1447x859.jpg&w=1920&q=75amp;qhttps://www.boltdesign.nyc/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2F4j6lg3tu%2Fproduction%2F52652e63365208885f555c81484ff15eb2155f66-1447x859.jpg&w=3840&q=75;w=3840&amp;q=75 2x" alt="Bar Design NYC, Bolt, Bolt Builds, Bolt Builds NYC, Bolt Builds New York City, Bolt Design NYC, Bolt New York City, Boutique Design Agency New York, Custom Interior Design New York, Custom millwork NYC, Elegant Hospitality Interiors NYC, High-End Bar Design NYC, High-End Interior Design Agency NYC, High-End Retail Design New York, High-end Millwork NYC, Hospitality, Hospitality Interior Design New York, Innovative Hospitality Solutions New York, Luxery Millwork NYC, Luxury Bar Design NYC, Luxury Hospitality Consultants NYC, Luxury Millwork NYC, NYC Residential Interior Designers, New York, New York City, New York Design and Branding for Hospitality, New York Hospitality Branding, New York Retail Interior Design, Sophisticated Branding Agency NYC, luxury Hospitality Design NYC" width="1447" height="859" class="absolute object-cover w-full h-full z-0 inset-0" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 300vw, (max-width: 1000px) 200vw, 100vw"/></div><div class="border-x flex-1 flex flex-col justify-end"></div></header><div class="z-20 relative bg-white"><div class="sticky top-0 invisible"><div class="px-unit absolute left-0 right-0 bg-white"><div class="pt-unit border-black border-b"></div></div></div><div class="px-unit"><div class="pt-unit border-black border-x"><div class="sticky top-unit"><div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-unit px-unit pt-2 pb-4"><div class="col-span-6 lg:col-span-3 pr-2"><p class="text-current font-body text-3xl">Construction Project Manager </p></div><div class="col-span-6 lg:col-span-2"><h3 class="text-current font-body text-md">February 4, 2026</h3></div></div></div><div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-unit px-unit pt-8 pb-unit"><div class="col-start-1 col-end-13 md:col-start-2 md:col-end-12 lg:col-start-4 lg:col-end-12 xl:col-start-4 xl:col-end-10"><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4"><strong>About Bolt</strong></p><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4">Bolt is a full-service <strong>Design + Build</strong> firm and fully insured <strong>General Contractor</strong> based in Brooklyn. We specialize in design-forward hospitality, retail, and residential projects that merge classical sensibility with innovative construction and fabrication methods. We believe that great design is only as strong as its execution — and that means being just as rigorous about budgets, schedules, and communication as we are about creative vision.</p><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4"></p><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4"><strong>The Role</strong></p><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4">Bolt is looking for a seasoned <strong>Construction Project Manager</strong> to lead construction operations across multiple high-impact job sites. This is a field-forward role for someone who thrives on-site, communicates with clarity and confidence, and brings rigor to budgets, timelines, and execution.</p><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4">You’ll interface directly with clients, subcontractors, and city agencies while managing a team of supers and ensuring projects are delivered at the highest standard.</p><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4">We’re a design-driven, detail-obsessed team — and we’re looking for someone who takes the same pride in building as we do in designing.</p><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4"></p><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4"><strong>What You’ll Do</strong></p><ul class="space-y-2"><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4"><strong>Own and manage project budgets</strong> from preconstruction through closeout, tracking costs daily, identifying risks early, and ensuring profitability across multiple active jobs</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Develop and maintain <strong>detailed construction schedules</strong> aligned with project milestones, client expectations, and resource availability</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Coordinate site activity across multiple teams, ensuring efficient sequencing and subcontractor performance</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Work closely with internal Project Managers to align budget, scope, and schedule, flagging scope gaps, change orders, and cost impacts proactively</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Lead subcontractor pricing, bid leveling, and contract negotiation</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Review architectural and technical drawings to ensure budget alignment and constructability in the field</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Oversee permitting, inspections, and regulatory approvals (DOB, FDNY, LPC, etc.)</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Uphold Bolt’s quality and safety standards across all job sites</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Represent Bolt in client and consultant meetings, providing confident, informed updates on budget status, timelines, and construction progress</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Contribute to the development of more efficient budgeting, forecasting, and project delivery systems within the company</li></ul><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4"></p><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4"><strong>What We’re Looking For</strong></p><ul class="space-y-2"><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4"><strong>10+ years of construction management experience</strong>, ideally with a focus on high-end interiors, hospitality, or complex commercial projects</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Proven track record managing <strong>project budgets, schedules, and subcontractors across multiple simultaneous job sites</strong></li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4"><strong>Deep knowledge of building systems, detailing, sequencing, and trade coordination</strong></li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4"><strong>Strong familiarity with NYC codes, approvals, and permitting processes</strong> (DOB, FDNY, LPC, etc.)</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Proficiency in Bluebeam and construction management platforms</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Highly organized and methodical — able to maintain control over timelines, costs, and teams under pressure</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Clear, confident communicator with polished client-facing and leadership skills</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Ability to lead field teams with authority and empathy, while maintaining accountability</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Hungry to do exceptional work and help shape the future of a design-forward, growing firm</li></ul><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4"></p><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4"><strong>Why Bolt</strong></p><ul class="space-y-2"><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4"><strong>See your work built — and built fast.</strong> At Bolt, you won’t be stuck pushing paper for years before seeing results. Our projects move quickly, and the work you put in becomes something real, tangible, and lasting.</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4"><strong>Be hands-on.</strong> You won’t be siloed behind a screen — you’ll be in the field, in meetings, on walk-throughs, and fully involved in the process from start to finish.</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4"><strong>Work in the heart of Greenpoint.</strong> Our studio is based in one of Brooklyn’s most creative neighborhoods — surrounded by great food, inspiring spaces, and a thriving design community.</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4"><strong>Join a company on the rise.</strong> Bolt is entering a new chapter of growth — and we’re building something special. You’ll help shape the future of the company, not just execute the present.</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4"><strong>Build projects you’re proud of.</strong> From thoughtful restaurants to bold retail environments, you’ll be part of a team that sweats the details and cares deeply about design, craft, and execution.</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4"><strong>Work with good people.</strong> We’re a tight-knit, driven team that takes pride in what we do — and has fun doing it. We value trust, accountability, and creative problem-solving.</li></ul><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4"></p><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4"><strong>Compensation</strong></p><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4">This is a full-time, in-person role based in our Greenpoint, Brooklyn studio.</p><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4">The base salary range for this position is $80,000–$105,000, depending on experience and qualifications. Bolt also offers performance-based bonus opportunities and clear pathways for professional growth.</p><div class="mt-16 pb-12"><div class="px-6 py-8 bg-faint text-center"><p class="text-current font-body text-xl">To apply for this job, please email your resume to<!-- --> <a href="mailto:hello@bolt.build" class="font-bold hover:text-blue transition-colors border-b border-current border-dotted">hello@bolt.build ↗</a>.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><footer class="bg-white pb-unit px-unit relative z-[1000]"><div class="bg-white border border-b border-black pt-unit pb-unit"><div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-unit px-unit"><div class="col-span-6 lg:col-span-3"><a class="text-current hover:text-yellow transition-colors" href="../index.html"><div class="w-[24px]"><div class="w-full "><svg width="100%" height="100%" viewBox="0 0 114 265" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><title>Bolt Design NYC Logo</title><path d="M38 0H0.5V208H76.5V265H114V56.5H38V0Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg></div></div></a></div><div class="col-start-7 col-end-13 lg:col-start-5 lg:col-end-7"><a class="block hover:text-yellow transition-colors" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&amp;query=202+Banker+Street+Brooklyn+NY+11222"><p class="text-current font-body text-md">202 Banker Street</p><p class="text-current font-body text-md">Brooklyn, NY 11222</p></a></div><div class="col